steps.instruction:
Can be found [here](https://ww4.publix.com/recipes-planning/aprons-recipes/spinach-artichoke-crab-salad)

### Prep
- Quarter the artichoke hearts 

### Steps
1. Chop crabmeat
2. drain artichoke hearts
3. Combine in large bowl: crab, artichoke, olives, pimientos, mustard, spinach dip, salt, and pepper until blended
4. Arrange spinach on serving plates
5.  Add one-fourth of crab mixture to center of spinach; top with alfalfa sprouts (if desired)
6. Cut tomatoes and eggs into wedges and arrange around crab salad (if desired). Serve
